data.description: NEW INTERIOR PAINT! NEW CARPET JUST INSTALLED on 2nd Floor! This beautiful 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home is located near Downtown Buckeye! Downstairs includes the Master Bedroom Suite, Large Kitchen, Great Room, Dining Room, & Breakfast Nook! All with Wood looking Tile! 2nd Floor includes 3 Bedrooms, full Bath, Bonus Room, & Laundry Room! New Carpet in Bedrooms and Bonus Room! The City of Buckeye is experiencing major growth at this time! Five Below & Funko Distribution Centers are 4 miles north on Miller Road. Kore Power is building its lithium-ion battery factory about 3 miles away! Ross For Less Distribution Center & several others are actively being built! The I-10 Freeway is 5 miles north & SR85 is less than 2 miles to the west! Welcome Home in the Nation's Fastest Growing City!
